<h2 class="mt-5">Why do we ask for this information?</h2>
<p>We ask for this information so that we can get in touch with you. We do not share your name, email, or phone number with bar prep companies when we ask them to submit a bid. However, we may share your name and email with select bar prep companies at other times, for example, to ensure you get any negotiated discounts.</p>
<p>We do not share your name, email, phone number or address with any third party for the purposes of directly marketing to you. You can find more information in our privacy policy.</p>
